@startuml dev-flow
title 開発フロー: 環境構築からビルド・テストまで

skinparam shadowing false
skinparam defaultFontName "Yu Gothic UI"
skinparam sequence {
  ArrowColor #555555
  LifeLineBorderColor #4A90E2
  ParticipantBorderColor #4A90E2
  ParticipantBackgroundColor #F0F7FF
  ActorBorderColor #555555
  ActorBackgroundColor #FFFFFF
}

actor "受講生" as user
participant "PowerShell\n(Windows)" as ps
participant "Bash\n(WSL2 Ubuntu)" as bash
participant "Podman" as podman
participant "Oracle XE\nコンテナ" as oracle
participant "Codex devbox\nコンテナ" as codex
participant "Maven\n(mvnw)" as mvn
participant "OpenAI API" as openai

== 初回セットアップ ==
user -> ps : .\\scripts\\setup.ps1
ps -> ps : WSL 機能有効化\nUbuntu 22.04 取得
ps --> user : 再起動指示
user -> bash : bash scripts/setup-wsl.sh
bash -> bash : Podman / JDK21 / Maven\nキャッシュ初期化
bash -> bash : scripts/build-codex-image.sh\n→ codex-devbox image
bash --> user : codex-shell エイリアス登録

== OracleDB 起動 ==
user -> bash : bash scripts/start-oracle.sh
bash -> podman : podman compose up -d oracle
podman -> oracle : 起動 (healthcheck.sh)
oracle -> oracle : 初期化スクリプト実行\n01_create_schema.sql
oracle --> podman : healthy
podman --> bash : ready
bash --> user : "Oracle XE is ready."

== Codex CLI で開発 ==
user -> bash : codex-shell
bash -> podman : podman run codex-devbox\n(--userns=keep-id)
podman -> codex : 起動 (/workspace bind)
user -> codex : 自然言語で指示
codex -> openai : HTTPS (gpt-5-codex)
openai --> codex : 提案コード
codex -> codex : apply_patch でファイル編集\n(sandbox: workspace-write)
codex --> user : 変更内容を確認

== テスト実行 (H2 軽量モード) ==
user -> codex : ./mvnw -B -Ph2 verify
codex -> mvn : Maven 起動
mvn -> mvn : Flyway 適用 → H2 mem\nJUnit + JaCoCo
mvn --> codex : BUILD SUCCESS / 失敗

== Oracle 統合テスト ==
user -> codex : ./mvnw -B -Plocal verify
codex -> mvn : Maven 起動 (profile=local)
mvn -> oracle : JDBC 接続\nlocalhost:1521/XEPDB1
mvn -> oracle : Flyway: V1__init.sql\nschema=TSUBUYAKI
mvn -> mvn : JUnit / Checkstyle / SpotBugs
mvn --> codex : BUILD SUCCESS
codex --> user : 結果報告 + 次の提案

@enduml
